sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as Demo.Bff or External OIDC Client
    participant Authorize as AuthorizeController
    participant ClientSvc as ClientService
    participant AuthSvc as AuthorizationService
    participant CodeRepo as AuthorizationCodeRepository
    participant Token as TokenController
    participant TokenSvc as TokenService

    Client->>Authorize: GET /connect/authorize
    Authorize->>ClientSvc: ValidateClientForAuthorizationAsync
    ClientSvc-->>Authorize: client + redirect_uri + PKCE 验证结果
    Authorize->>Authorize: 检查登录态 / prompt / consent / max_age
    Authorize->>AuthSvc: GenerateCodeAsync
    AuthSvc->>CodeRepo: AddAsync(authorization_code)
    CodeRepo-->>AuthSvc: 持久化完成
    AuthSvc-->>Authorize: 返回 code
    Authorize-->>Client: 302 redirect_uri?code=...&state=...

    Client->>Token: POST /connect/token<br/>grant_type=authorization_code
    Token->>ClientSvc: AuthenticateClientAsync
    ClientSvc-->>Token: 客户端认证通过
    Token->>AuthSvc: ValidateAndConsumeCodeAsync
    AuthSvc->>CodeRepo: FindByCodeAsync + MarkUsedAsync
    AuthSvc-->>Token: 返回 user_id / scope / nonce / claims
    Token->>TokenSvc: IssueAccessTokenWithMetadataAsync
    Token->>TokenSvc: IssueRefreshTokenAsync
    Token->>TokenSvc: IssueIdTokenAsync
    TokenSvc-->>Token: access_token + refresh_token + id_token
    Token-->>Client: 返回 token 响应
